    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Demo Version</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Veliri </strong>is a hardcore 2D MMO in a sandbox world where you can become a trader, mercenary, pirate, or explorer. Here's what awaits you:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full-loot </strong>— the better your gear, the more valuable your loot.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open PvP </strong>— only bases are safe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complex mechanics </strong>— you'll have to study and analyze to survive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unforgiving controls </strong>— skill comes with practice.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We're constantly improving the game, but harshness is part of its soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras/e4c93e715461f84119acb134e5fc682a.poster.avif?t=1767282063\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras/e4c93e715461f84119acb134e5fc682a.webm?t=1767282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras/e4c93e715461f84119acb134e5fc682a.mp4?t=1767282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The demo version does not include the full storyline (except the introductory part), and may contain localization errors or other technical imperfections.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The servers run on home PCs in Europe – remote players may experience high ping and occasional outages, but we’ll fix everything! :)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Even if you play solo, the world of Veliri stays alive:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade NPCs maintain the economy, even when few players are online.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras/40156240443c46b9d39591ec6e3b61f5.avif?t=1767282063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras_big/40156240443c46b9d39591ec6e3b61f5.avif?t=1767282063 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bots gather resources, transport cargo, wage wars, and even chat with each other.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras/a4a5337ba8f1f0cb0239746c2cce6178.poster.avif?t=1767282063\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras/a4a5337ba8f1f0cb0239746c2cce6178.webm?t=1767282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras/a4a5337ba8f1f0cb0239746c2cce6178.mp4?t=1767282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Constant territorial battles and spontaneous skirmishes :)<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras/71b0d7add4b3199b7fbece881733e62b.poster.avif?t=1767282063\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras/71b0d7add4b3199b7fbece881733e62b.webm?t=1767282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras/71b0d7add4b3199b7fbece881733e62b.mp4?t=1767282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real-time combat with a non-target system<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras/9c3223a6c3bed19c0d0ff3e80d1df275.poster.avif?t=1767282063\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras/9c3223a6c3bed19c0d0ff3e80d1df275.webm?t=1767282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100340/extras/9c3223a6c3bed19c0d0ff3e80d1df275.mp4?t=1767282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Do you dare to survive on this planet? Veliri awaits you!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p>",
